{"tid":880474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 有乜方法叫朋友還錢","createTime":"2018-10-28T17:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T23:47:30.000Z","uid":76355,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e48a1c197a190d6207def5bb776f2ccddcc6b03f","tid":880474,"uid":76355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:25:19.000Z","msg":"朋友借左我一萬蚊，差不多成年，提都無提過下<br />\n<br />\n咁佢係外國生活既，一個人半工讀話無錢交學費，一開始同情佢先借比佢，見到幾好人諗住實無死啦<br />\n<br />\n屌那星，呢一年見佢又買iphonex 旅行 食好西 返香港玩 仲要on99咁係ig放閃，究竟幾厚面皮先做得出？<br />\n<br />\n求教有乜方法可以叫佢還錢，雖然唔等錢洗但諗起好炆<br />\n<br />\nbtw 大家都係女仔，2x歲，識超過10年"},{"pid":"70f4e522e85321175b0669634e1ad52b5e4367a2","tid":880474,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:30:29.000Z","msg":"明顯佢係唔想還比妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b65d969b4a11223d6515ec246b3ba6cff78911c","tid":880474,"uid":209715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"求教有乜方法可以叫佢還錢：「喂還番一萬蚊比我」"},{"pid":"2e3b0445160b5960391deee37d96a4febb3c4f54","tid":880474,"uid":76355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f4e522e85321175b0669634e1ad52b5e4367a2","tid":880474,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:30:29.000Z","msg":"明顯佢係唔想還比妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:32:47.000Z","msg":"還錢如乞米，有乜高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49544f502d93583e20ea9539dd060c72814d9ec9","tid":880474,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你朋友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：還錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：ok"},{"pid":"9faa53d52899b3ffa3